{"tid":822020,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"一級颱風 英國人在作準備措施","createTime":"2018-09-16T06:42:57.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-16T18:51:32.000Z","uid":138134,"like":28,"dislike":118,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"1091cc602b9cb6f42dca6f991874426b9e8fed74","tid":822020,"uid":138134,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:42:57.000Z","msg":"一級颱風，英國人買雨衣、帶雨傘；香港人正常返工，不以為然。<br />\n<br />\n二級颱風，法國人買定儲糧；香港人係辦工室OT。<br />\n<br />\n三級颱風，菲律賓人買定救生艇，香港人排隊放工，等巴士。<br />\n<br />\n四級颱風，美國人啲屋吹到甩皮甩骨；香港人去海邊觀浪。<br />\n<br />\n五級颱風，東南亞地區變成洪水處處，美國變成明日之後；香港人終於話：『係時候搶定糧食，返屋企貼下膠紙』<br />\n連登仔：『攞住午餐肉有西屌啲日子來了！去旺角裸跑先！』"},{"pid":"44b14fb34d1a3dec23046a2a3fe13076381ffc3e","tid":822020,"uid":52984,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:44:22.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"9ef028955e51f2040e5ffcc0ba005496c1cc28cc","tid":822020,"uid":92376,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:45:04.000Z","msg":"-100/10"},{"pid":"31b5e83ae7a2c4ac54ba2130326fe5712656f597","tid":822020,"uid":42188,"like":27,"dislike":1,"score":26,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:45:06.000Z","msg":"好尷尬"},{"pid":"05058232a95c1788451f3de3b132f176f5b8935f","tid":822020,"uid":50744,"like":9,"dislike":4,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:49:58.000Z","msg":"慨念唔錯<br />\n膠力不足<br />\n1.5/10"},{"pid":"99140cebd1008f08eb07458020898c5b99ad0dbf","tid":822020,"uid":160916,"like":0,"dislike":9,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T06:59:48.000Z","msg":"我覺得ok<br />\n<br />\n4/10"},{"pid":"322d8656d205a1a2df1d95702a2218c14e52b70b","tid":822020,"uid":45613,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:06:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 打風先lm<br />\n0分"},{"pid":"052f984dc5e8b71560a6fd3e89a79f8510786265","tid":822020,"uid":90506,"like":1,"dislike":7,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-16T07:09:36.000Z","msg":"我覺得最後裸跑幾好<br />\n6.5/10"},{"pid":"86fcd3450debbe371